lead_paragraph: Nazem Kadri scored two of his three goals during second-period power plays and the Toronto Maple Leafs beat the Florida Panthers 5-2 on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Kadri Gets Hat Trick, Maple Leafs Beat Panthers 5-2
